column5: Spent a week in Sturgeon Falls visiting Folks and a few days fishing the shallow waters.  Lots of pike and amazing perch. Hope these pics turn out, first time uploading, had to re-size.     Peace, Nuke
WTG Nice looking Perch hope i get an invite to the fish fry!!!LOL Thanks for sharing
man, that bottom one is a pig!!!!!!   way to go.  jason
Wow man! I have never seen Perch like that! Thanks for the shots.
yup, those are some nice looking jumbos.
Beauty perch.  Did you measure the girth of that one on the bottom?  Looks like a severly overinflated football, wow.
Those are some nice perch they will make a nice meal  rob
Nice perch, that ones a real fatty.
:clapping:   Those look like Cache Bay perch to me !!!      Nice Catch!!  That's where this was taken..

Hey Randy, when you thought Cache Bay, were you looking through your cristal ball  ? That's where I was.  I see you are doing well.  The perch seemed to have moved now.  Maybe stopped feeding for the spawn ?  Peace, Nuke
